{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-chapter-level-2-chapter-level-2-tsx","path":"/topics/childhood-cancers-recognition-referral/diagnosis/symptoms-suggestive-of-childhood-cancers/","result":{"pageContext":{"chapter":{"id":"2e4faf68-8401-5c16-9d89-770cc18882a3","slug":"symptoms-suggestive-of-childhood-cancers","fullItemName":"Symptoms suggestive of childhood cancers","depth":2,"htmlHeader":"<!-- begin field 30cf1176-fbed-4b31-93a3-e83bffeedead --><h2>Symptoms suggestive of childhood cancers</h2><!-- end field 30cf1176-fbed-4b31-93a3-e83bffeedead -->","summary":"","htmlStringContent":"<!-- begin item c98aa293-80d3-4b50-82ff-1c5810629955 --><!-- begin field 08f68d6e-0b92-4b77-9422-5f70e69e7706 --><p><strong>Table 1. </strong>Symptoms suggestive of childhood cancers.</p><table data-table-id=\"c118d081-9147-4b88-a555-acce014f3a3e\"><thead><tr><th>Symptom</th><th>Possible cancer</th><th>Referral recommendation</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td>Abdominal mass (palpable) or enlarged abdominal organ (unexplained) in children</td><td>Neuroblastoma or Wilms' tumour</td><td>Consider a very urgent referral (for an appointment within 48 hours) for specialist assessment</td></tr><tr><td>Haematuria (visible and unexplained) in children</td><td>Wilms' tumour</td><td>Consider a very urgent referral (for an appointment within 48 hours) for specialist assessment</td></tr><tr><td>Absent red reflex in children</td><td>Retinoblastoma</td><td>Consider urgent referral (for an appointment within 2 weeks) for ophthalmological assessment</td></tr><tr><td>Parental or carer insight, concern or anxiety about the child's or young person's symptoms (persistent)</td><td>Childhood cancers</td><td><p>Take into account the insight and knowledge of parents and carers when considering making a referral for suspected cancer in a child or young person</p><p>Consider referral for children if their parent or carer has persistent concern or anxiety about the child's symptoms, even if the symptoms are most likely to have a benign cause</p></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"3\"><p><strong>Data from:</strong> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/childhood-cancers-recognition-referral/references/\">NICE, 2015</a>]</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p> </p><!-- end field 08f68d6e-0b92-4b77-9422-5f70e69e7706 --><!-- end item c98aa293-80d3-4b50-82ff-1c5810629955 -->","topic":{"id":"7ea64737-af89-5cad-8f33-2466d98eab3a","topicId":"360677c6-0adf-45e4-87f1-98b0ab02c557","topicName":"Childhood cancers - recognition and referral","slug":"childhood-cancers-recognition-referral","lastRevised":"Last revised in February 2021","chapters":[{"id":"3a84248b-68fe-535d-a2c8-570960c744af","fullItemName":"Summary","slug":"summary","subChapters":[]},{"id":"6172d98b-b3d3-59d4-bfcb-f0d787673884","fullItemName":"Have I got the right topic?","slug":"have-i-got-the-right-topic","subChapters":[]},{"id":"82d59d36-e24e-5089-8870-952cec58c93b","fullItemName":"How up-to-date is this topic?","slug":"how-up-to-date-is-this-topic","subChapters":[{"id":"951de1cf-297e-5e28-90f7-2b482a3f73d4","slug":"changes","fullItemName":"Changes"},{"id":"93b60b97-3e26-5b64-a493-791a75266270","slug":"update","fullItemName":"Update"}]},{"id":"43a3c8ca-4187-59d9-b1af-842bda4159f8","fullItemName":"Goals and outcome measures","slug":"goals-outcome-measures","subChapters":[{"id":"311645ef-ef46-5c04-a220-135331185f90","slug":"goals","fullItemName":"Goals"},{"id":"25f3b274-a4d7-5071-9854-87246c3a13d6","slug":"outcome-measures","fullItemName":"Outcome measures"},{"id":"d04c3c26-8145-5dd2-9e26-642ebe9403d7","slug":"audit-criteria","fullItemName":"Audit criteria"},{"id":"2ae9f6b6-9722-5f17-b601-6f5ca8bbc2eb","slug":"qof-indicators","fullItemName":"QOF indicators"},{"id":"6ea5d6b9-bf9c-5af9-a190-d7e85fff8f9e","slug":"qipp-options-for-local-implementation","fullItemName":"QIPP - Options for local implementation"},{"id":"c18ccf4b-f36f-5964-9349-a4df758477cf","slug":"nice-quality-standards","fullItemName"